    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.19 * tmp + 0.81)) - ((tmp + 0.99 - v2 + 0.67) / v0))
    v1 = (0.17 / ((v0 + 0.74 * v1 + 0.62) * v2))
    v1 = 0.93
    v1 = wp.abs((wp.exp(tmp + 0.14) * wp.exp(v0 + 0.52)))
    v2 = wp.exp(wp.abs(wp.exp(tmp + 0.96)))
    v2 = (wp.cos((tmp + 0.93 + v1 + 0.38)) / wp.cos((v1 + 0.99 + v1 + 0.60)))
    data[tid] = v0
